{"tid":1542793,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【核彈】831失蹤義士與黃婆婆","createTime":"2019-09-05T03:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T03:28:41.000Z","uid":153771,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"244b4b16364540b0a0331dd73d9cd1da0fadc001","tid":1542793,"uid":153771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:28:32.000Z","msg":"大家當焦點放係831失蹤義士嘅時候，本來已經有嘅核彈就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃婆婆失左蹤</span></span>，黃婆婆企幾前，見過佢幾多次大家知，自黃婆被狗拘捕之後，完全無左聲氣，什至無人搵到佢，（希望係炒車）<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃婆婆有機會已被消失</span></span>，將831同黃婆婆兩件事聯想埋一齊，如果現場有人權組織，過長封站時間，突然宣布撤回條例，可能真係有人已經死左。<br />\n<br />\n人權組織係現場 推到開記招<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkhrm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkhrm%2F&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6rucv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=c564c3c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkhrm/</a>"},{"pid":"e41b6c867a2ace3df6c9965e45473731cdd00144","tid":1542793,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:28:41.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=